; Trimmed sample mirroring the idokapu.svx structure: a *data passage block
; preceded by per-column *units overrides where one column is in feet.

*begin idokapu
  *date 2025.10.08
  *team "acca,joe"
  *units tape meter
  *units compass degree
  *units clino degree
  *alias station - ..
  *flags not splay
  *data normal from to tape compass clino
    0 1 1.37 92.0 1.4
    1 2 0.68 150.1 64.6
    0 10 22.00 2.0 2.0
  *flags not splay

*units left feet
*units right meter
*units up meter
*units down meter
*data passage station left right up down
1   0.07 0.36 0.35 0.29
2   1.20 0.38 1.45 0.00
0   0.17 0.35 3.00 4.00
10  0.00 0.00 0.00 0.00

*end idokapu
